S.FORM: Swaziland hya' ga cyux maki' tay 26 30 S, 31 30 E na Xweco syuw. kwara' kinghciyan niya' 17,364 sq km (maki' tay 159ginkgan kin wahci') (kinwhci' niya' ga 17,204 sq km, kinwhci' na lawsayan wsilung hya' ga 160 sq km) Kinkhmayan kwara' squliq hya' ga 1,451,428. Pinbcyan naha' sni' naha' rhzyal hya' iy pqmahun hya' ga 68.30%, lhlahuy hya' ga 31.70%, sni' naha' sa pptzyuwaw sa bzinah hya' ga 0%. spzyang qalang na Kokka' spzyang naha' krahu' qalang hya' ga Mbabane. snyan kinramat inlungan na Kokka' snyan kinramat inlungan na Kokka' hya' ga 6 na tay mqiru' byacing na qutux kawas. mrhuw Kokka' mrhuw Kokka' ta' misuw hya' ga Mswati III, aring ryax 25 squ byacing tay 4 sa kawas 1986 lga, musa' spazyang balay ms'rux kya la. cinkhulan sa knita' sa brbiru' CIA 外交部
